author: cmpilato
msg: Turn on binary property support in the server->client direction.
Clients will learn to transmit in the next milestone, and then this
issue (issue #1015) will be (finally) finished.
* subversion/mod_dav_svn/deadprops.c
(dav_svn_db_output_value): No longer conditionalize the binary prop
support.
* subversion/tests/clients/cmdline/prop_tests.py
(test_list): No longer skip 'binary_props' test.  Note that that
test still has a workaround for making it actually run over
ra_dav, which will also be removed in the next milestone.

author: cmpilato
msg: * subversion/bindings/swig/swigutil_py.c

hopefully this will work on Windows now.
